# Where the sync client sends requests. Normally leave this UNSET: one Cloudflare Worker serves both
# the app and the sync API, so sync defaults to same-origin. Set a URL only to point at a different
# origin, or set it to empty to disable sync (local-only). Public value, not a secret.
# VITE_SYNC_URL=https://questline.<your-subdomain>.workers.dev
